# The iOS app is its own repository (pochtmanr/physicsios), checked out here so
# it sits beside the web app and the docs/prompts it is built from. It is NOT a
# submodule — this repo simply ignores it.
# Leading slash matters: a bare `ios/` would also swallow `scripts/ios/`, which
# belongs to THIS repo (the scene-snapshot pipeline).
/ios/
